value.original: Sets which of the 3 possible types the event is: *Close. This event is triggered by Cash Up process in case the payment type allows automatic movement of founds. It is used to determine the destination financial account for these movements. *In. Used by Cash Management process for deposits. When a deposit is done, the list of available In events for that payment type is shown to select one of them. Financial account in the event is used as origin account, this is, the amount will be taken from this account and deposited in the terminal's account. *Out. Used by Cash Management process for withdrawals. When a withdrawals is done, the list of available Out events for that payment type is shown to select one of them. Financial account in the event is used as destination account, this is, the amount will be taken from terminal's account and deposited on this account.
